               <head>Pentateuch</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/n79066420" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>The Pentatuech with vowel-points and accents, masorah magna and parva. Sefer ha-tigan is prefixed.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="jrb-Hebr">Hebrew, Judeo-Arabic</textLang>
                  
                  
                  
